Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Rin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vatican headquarters? High Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my license and my level certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you really are who you say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Middle Class Exorcist Kaoru Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah whatever... I hate formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm taking this kid to the Japanese Branch Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanna talk to the head of the branch, Mephisto,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so bring him along even if you've gotta use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up already. I have a shitload of stuff I wanna ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is injured. Could you wait until we give him first aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine. And kids who still smell of milk should stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Smell of milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's mission is over. Please head back to your dormitories right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh damn, I'm so jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who's that babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Yamada, isn't she? She's wearing male uniform trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That Okumura, did he get into trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know  but it's not Rin's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You've never been to the base, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The center of the Japanese Branch of the Order of True Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The headquarters are under St. Peter's Basilica in Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it coordinates the actions of the branches around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order's history in exorcism spans over two millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Japanese Branch of the Order of True Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Shura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that a High Inspector would infiltrate the cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto, gimme a straight answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hide him. It was all for the sake of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the Order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tame the son of Satan to become a weapon for the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We Exorcists have been on the defensive for 2000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,now is our chance to take the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asking why you didn't report to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, his powers are still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gregori wouldn't be satisfied with something incomplete, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shiro Fujimoto have anything to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything? He was raising him until his flames got stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just keeping an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Either way, I'll have to report this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that I gotta interrogate him. I'll use the Great Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to. He's a real laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so relaxed. You'll be sorry for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shura, wait! It's pointless to question my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure haven't changed, Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well okay, you {\i1}did{\i0\fscx140} {\r}get taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the trouble, go home and hit your bunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure were meek like a scared little kitty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew my dad and Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I was Shiro Fujimoto's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you a nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately I've never once prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in a place outside the range of reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro Fujimoto saved me from staying alive every day just for the sake of staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That was way before you two were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did you get hurt earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! How could you fall for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this shit so cheap you'll let anyone take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword is still sheathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Demon-Slaying Blade can't suppress his power completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to take that scaredy four-eyes as my pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're familiar with using demon swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to give him a demon sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving a demon sword to a child is insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If something ever happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, teach him how to use his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? You were so cool and strong and perfect, what happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared because you saw a glance of the end of your road?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You threw me away, and now you want to push that kid on me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you. Never show yourself in front of me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro... I wanted to believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to believe that you're the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sever the head of the snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that devours the eight princesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why would my dad's apprentice point her sword at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The day Shiro died the Vatican headquarters dispatched me as High Inspector with secret orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is a possibility that Shiro Fujimoto and Mephisto Pheles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the head of the Japanese Branch, have been hiding something related to Satan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,since the Blue Night 16 years ago. Investigate that."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"And if by chance there was such an element,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you are hereby authorized to eliminate it upon identification."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed your blue flames, the sign of Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll obey my orders and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The apprentice will finish her dead master's incomplete work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirigakure Demon Sword Technique: Snakefang!{Davos}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they've started. Don't even bother trying to go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Cell can only be opened by High Class Exorcists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We are to quietly wait until the interrogation ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like with that demon earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our levels are totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you oppose the Vatican by hiding Satan's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tame the son of Satan to become a weapon for the Order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you tried to accomplish and lost your life for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a big mistake. This blunt and untempered kid wouldn't even scratch Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got old, Shiro. You gave up fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and clung to some pointless hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He died protecting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was no coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything! How dare you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you were his apprentice or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you make fun of my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes a lot of useless moves and he looks like he's got no idea of proper fighting techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Didn't you say you won't let me make fun of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't come at me, I'll have at you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirigakure Demon Sword Technique: Emptiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so ugly... Just go down already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed on his grave that I'd become a great Exorcist like him and kick Satan's filthy ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick Satan's ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll become the strongest Exorcist and Paladin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become Paladin everyone will have to accept that he was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Paladin, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh you shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a laugh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right... He {\i1}is{\i0\fscx140} {\r}a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess the joke's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You loved Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not like I didn't!{tsuntsun}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro, you weren't raising weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were raising a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! That stings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,30,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,30,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,30,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,30,,Just look at it. A wooden sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,30,,And my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,37,,{\q2}I'll take care of it. If it's with you,\N\NAmaimon will just come to play with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it back, get stronger. You'll get it back once you can kick my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you gotta prove that Shiro was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll postpone my report to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'll continue watching over Rin Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, get a place for me at the Japanese Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so delighted to welcome such a renowned Exorcist like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wonderful green tea ice cream from Uji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto... Just what the hell are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My only wish is peace for humankind and Assiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I abandoned Gehenna and came here to serve that goal .
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you're a demon and the higher-ups don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Brother, it looks like they have no trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaimon... I have plenty to discuss with you regarding this case.{uses the same yama hodo as shura's earlier shitload}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, what are you doing so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad? Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, calm down! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Leave me alone! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you've just done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You beat up your friends and they are suffering in a hospital now.{beeing Rin's friend is suffering}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me a monster and they mocked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for being so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you raise a child like that? He really looks like a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand back. This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Da-Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As if! Just kidding! You got scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rin. If you keep on like this, you'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your strength for someone else... For some gentler purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to become a cool guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with lots of friends and who's loved by the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean... How can I be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle! If you try hard to be nice to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one day you'll become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Mr. Fujimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have broken ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you look at me like that! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A tiny fist like yours can't knock me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But your ribs are broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke them on purpose. To match the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have them checked out by some boobie-wonder nurses!{mfw}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be a cool adult like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get it... Why are Father and Brother so obsessed with him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to become a weapon for the Order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you gotta prove that Shiro was right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not smart enough to figure out the answers no matter how much time I spend thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Blackie! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do now is to empty my head and {rainbow }dash forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dispatched by the Vatican headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shura Kirigakure, 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was taking classes with you guys for the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of teaching you magic circles, seals and... Oh damn, even swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Suguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you disguise yourself as a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Adult matters. None of you kids' business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss! Professor Neuhaus was our teacher for that class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he be transferred in the middle of the term?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on maternity leave! Maternity!{I fucking love Shura}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Neuhaus is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he can still take a break to take care of the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh whatever. Just ask the Principal if you care about it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I... couldn't sleep yesterday... and I fell asleep on the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one woke me up even when the homeroom ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there with your excuses, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get to your seat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, are your wounds okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, I'm fine, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow he seems different.{in my arse}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened?{he was carried off with his face in boobs. hmm.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're all here, let's start the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Introduction to {the Study of }Sigils, from the part about mammomancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura, because you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it to become Paladin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... In relation to sauces about ancient geomancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.79,0:24:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my fault.
