Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,980)}(WIRED...)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:40.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,0)}I'm lightly fluttering in wondrous light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:44.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,440)}like a dancing butterfly in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:48.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,500)}Is this place in another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:53.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,820)}My fall isn't slowing down so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.63,0:22:56.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(220,480)}cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The numbers that make my head spin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,230)}are forming a rising spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:07.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:14.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:18.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:25.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:33.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:35.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:37.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}wired life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:40.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.89,0:23:45.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:55.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,900)}There is wired life.
